	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001055_0001"/><!--pb/@n='61r'-->
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="2" unit="chars"/><placeName>Hadley Green</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>6<hi rend="sup">th</hi> July 1857</p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Murray</persName></p>
<lb/><p>Thanks for 
<lb/>the drawing of the 
<lb/>Falls which came 
<lb/>safely. I enclose 
<lb/>a note from my brother to 
<lb/>your banker 
<lb/>about the money 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001055_0002"/><!--pb/@n='61v'--> 
<lb/>we sent (Â£30) to 
<lb/><placeName>Boston</placeName> as <persName>Blake 
<lb/>Howe &amp; Co.</persName> of 
<lb/>that city told <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi>
<lb/>C. Livingstone</persName> on 
<lb/>16<hi rend="sup">th</hi> June that 
<lb/>they had advised <persName>Herries &amp; Co</persName> to 
<lb/>pay it to <persName>C. Livingstone</persName>
<lb/>in <placeName>London</placeName>. He 
<lb/>still wants it 
<lb/>paid to his wife 
<lb/>in <placeName>America</placeName><reg>.</reg>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001055_0003"/><!--pb/@n='62r'--> 
<lb/>Will you forward the enclosed to 
<lb/>your Bankers<reg>?</reg></p>
<lb/><p>I have manuscript 
<lb/>which I shall either 
<lb/>bring <add place="above">to you</add> or send to 
<lb/><placeName>1 Robert St. Adelphi</placeName>
<lb/>tomorrow. I think 
<lb/>two or three more 
<lb/>than what I bring 
<lb/>tomorrow will 
<lb/>be the end. I am 
<lb/>going down the <placeName>Zambesi</placeName>
<lb/>to <placeName>Tete</placeName> now<reg>.</reg>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001055_0004"/><!--pb/@n='62v'--> 
<lb/>I shall bring <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> L</persName>
<lb/>to <persName>Sir Henry Holland</persName>
<lb/>the first time I come<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>Will you send to 
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Taylor</persName><placeName>1 Robert 
<lb/>St. Adelphi</placeName> if 
<lb/>I do not come 
<lb/>before 3 o<reg>'</reg>clock<reg>?</reg>
<lb/>I shall bring 
<lb/>Kane. </p>
<lb/><p>Yours &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
			
</div>
